# This project needs NO secrets to run.
#
# The forecasting loop only uses Kalshi's PUBLIC market-data endpoints (markets,
# events, series, orderbooks), which require no authentication. Discovery, price
# refresh, and resolution reconciliation all work with no key. There is no .env to
# create for normal use.
#
# OPTIONAL — only if you later add Kalshi ACCOUNT features (portfolio/balance/orders,
# which this read-only, paper-only project deliberately does NOT use). If set, the
# client will RSA-sign requests; if unset, it simply skips signing.
#   KALSHI_KEY_ID=
#   KALSHI_PRIVATE_KEY=        # PEM; literal \n between lines is accepted
#
# OPTIONAL — cap the heavier bootstrap (first) run to N markets.
#   FIRST_RUN_MAX=10
